{"tid":2247644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「蒙古討論」復旦大學教授權威宣布：成吉思汗是漢人，震驚世界","createTime":"2020-10-18T04:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T02:31:20.000Z","uid":30561,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fcba3c069c1e3ac97c5e9446882d8b305347c0","tid":2247644,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"復旦大學教授宣布：基因測試表明，成吉思汗是漢人<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/3x4x96a.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2F3x4x96a.html&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=b065694b\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/3x4x96a.html</a><br />\n<br />\n復旦大學研究稱成吉思汗是漢人，這類研究的邏輯嚴謹嗎？<br />\n<br />\n具體到成吉思汗的後代的Y染色體類型這個科學問題，目前在嚴肅的科硏論文和數據裏也有不少了。李輝指的O3下面的M117，這確實是漢族最大的類型，但蒙古尤其內蒙古也有一些。另外的硏究還有支持C3*星簇（現在已經更新成C3b2b-F3273，主要在草原民族，漢族很少）或C3d（也已更新名稱，目前是C&alpha;1a1-M407，這個在漢族或北方民族都有一定分佈）是成吉思汗所屬支系的，目前數據裏O3a1c-002611（漢族的大類，內蒙的蒙族也有）的樣本也有一些。<br />\n<br />\n另外關於蒙古西征，拔都係沙皇？忽必烈從來不是蒙古大汗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_2kLw-vlTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc_2kLw-vlTY&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=e712d469\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_2kLw-vlTY</a><br />\n<br />\n蒙古西征1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QimzkISAWg0&amp;list=PL2gmihcScOItX-sVq6OLL7oY20NA01kYL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQimzkISAWg0%26list%3DPL2gmihcScOItX-sVq6OLL7oY20NA01kYL&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=8374d311\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QimzkISAWg0&amp;list=PL2gmihcScOItX-sVq6OLL7oY20NA01kYL</a><br />\n<br />\n蒙古西征2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kqUMObzuao&amp;list=PL2gmihcScOItX-sVq6OLL7oY20NA01kYL&amp;index=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7kqUMObzuao%26list%3DPL2gm